comment:
* Pno network to be added to the PNO scan filtering.
         * {@hide}

variables.name: FLAG_DIRECTED_SCAN
variables.comment: Whether directed scan needs to be performed (for hidden SSIDs)

variables.name: FLAG_A_BAND
variables.comment: Whether PNO event shall be triggered if the network is found on A band

variables.name: FLAG_G_BAND
variables.comment: Whether PNO event shall be triggered if the network is found on G band

variables.name: FLAG_STRICT_MATCH
variables.comment:
* Whether strict matching is required
             * If required then the firmware must store the network's SSID and not just a hash

variables.name: FLAG_SAME_NETWORK
variables.comment:
* If this SSID should be considered the same network as the currently connected
             * one for scoring.

variables.name: frequencies
variables.comment: frequencies on which the particular network needs to be scanned for
